\c 2
\s Iminikelo yokudla
\p
\v 1 Lalapho umuntu enikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni umnikelo wokudla\x + 6.14; 9.17. Nani 15.4.\x*, umnikelo wakhe uzakuba ngowempuphu ecolekileyo; abesethela amafutha phezu kwawo, abeke inhlaka kuwo,
\v 2 awulethe kumadodana kaAroni, abapristi, acuphe kuwo isandla sakhe esigcweleyo impuphu yawo ecolekileyo lokwamafutha awo, kanye lenhlaka yawo yonke; lompristi atshise isikhumbuzo sawo elathini, umnikelo\x + 2.10. Eks. 40.10.\x* owenziwe ngomlilo, oloqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1.9,16; 5.12; 6.15; 24.7; Isa. 66.3; Seb. 10.4.\x*.
\v 3 Lokuseleyo komnikelo wokudla kuzakuba ngokukaAroni lokwamadodana akhe\x + 7.9; 10.12,13.\x*; kuyingcwelengcwele\x + 2.10. Eks. 40.10.\x* eminikelweni yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo.
\p
\v 4 Nxa uletha-ke umnikelo womnikelo wokudla ophekwe eziko, kawube ngowamaqebelengwana angelamvubelo empuphu ecolekileyo ahlanganiswe lamafutha\x + Eks. 29.2.\x*, loba izinkwana eziyizipatalala ezingelamvubelo ezinindwe ngamafutha.
\p
\v 5 Uba-ke umnikelo wakho ungumnikelo wokudla \add ophekwe\add* ngomganu oyincence, uzakuba ngowempuphu ecolekileyo engelamvubelo, ixubene lamafutha.
\v 6 Uwuhlephune ube yizihlephu, uthele amafutha kuzo; kungumnikelo wokudla.
\p
\v 7 Uba-ke umnikelo wakho ungumnikelo wokudla \add ophekwe\add* ngembiza\x + 7.9.\x*, kuzakwenziwa ngempuphu ecolekileyo kanye lamafutha.
\v 8 Njalo uzaletha umnikelo wokudla owenziwe ngalezizinto eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; nxa ulethwa kumpristi, uzawuletha elathini.
\v 9 Umpristi uzathatha emnikelweni wokudla isikhumbuzo sawo\x + 2.2.\x*, asitshise elathini; singumnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo, oloqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 10 Lokuseleyo komnikelo wokudla\x + 2.3.\x* kuzakuba ngokukaAroni lokwamadodana akhe; kuyingcwelengcwele eminikelweni yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo.
\v 11 Kakulamnikelo wokudla elizawuletha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ozakwenziwa ngemvubelo\x + 6.17. Mat. 16.12. Mark. 8.15. Luka 12.1. 1 Kor. 5.8. Gal. 5.9.\x*, ngoba kawuyikutshisa langayiphi imvubelo loba ngaluphi uluju umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\p
\v 12 Umnikelo wezithelo zokuqala\x + Eks. 23.19.\x* lizawunikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kodwa kawuyikutshiswa elathini kube luqhatshi olumnandi.
\v 13 Lawo wonke umnikelo womnikelo wakho wokudla uzawutshwaya ngetshwayi\x + Mark. 9.49,50. Kol. 4.6.\x*; njalo ungavumeli ukuthi itshwayi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu wakho\x + Nani 18.19. 2 Lan. 13.5.\x* lisweleke emnikelweni wakho wokudla; kanye leminikelo yakho yonke\x + Hez. 43.24.\x* uzanikela itshwayi.
\v 14 Uba-ke unikela umnikelo wokudla wezithelo zokuqala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uzanikela kube ngumnikelo wokudla ezithelweni zakho zokuqala amabele amatsha ayizikhwebu ezosiweyo\x + 23.14. Josh. 5.11.\x*, amabele achotshoziweyo ezikhwebu ezintsha\x + 23.14; 2 Kho. 4.42.\x*;
\v 15 uthele amafutha kuwo\x + 2.1.\x*, ubeke inhlaka phezu kwawo; kungumnikelo wokudla.
\v 16 Umpristi uzatshisa-ke isikhumbuzo sawo\x + 2.2.\x*, okwamabele achotshoziweyo awo lokwamafutha awo, layo yonke inhlaka yawo; kungumnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.